     "data": {
      "text/markdown": [
       "### Detect the single-steppers\n",
       "Here I select BB light curves with exactly two blocks, and record the ratio\n",
       "of the two levels (the steps), and the position of the transition.\n",
       "The light curves were generated with a bin width of 7 days, so the \"step\" position\n",
       "must be at a bin boundary, the boundary position depending on the BB algorithm, its uncertainty TBD.\n",
       "Ratios close to 1.0 are possibly an artifact of the BB procedure, this needs study."
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "<utilities.ipynb_docgen.doc_formatter.<locals>.MimeBundleObject at 0x773c964965f0>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
